nd most third-party MagSafe brands.\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"sfaq-item\">\n        <button class=\"sfaq-btn\" type=\"button\">\n          Which iPhones are supported?\n          <span class=\"sfaq-icon\">+<\/span>\n        <\/button>\n        <div class=\"sfaq-answer\">\n          iPhone 12, 13, 14, 15, and 16 — all models (standard, Plus, Pro, and Pro Max). It uses the built-in MagSafe magnet array, so no adapter or modification is needed.\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"sfaq-item\">\n        <button class=\"sfaq-btn\" type=\"button\">\n          Will it affect autofocus or image quality?\n          <span class=\"sfaq-icon\">+<\/span>\n        <\/button>\n        <div class=\"sfaq-answer\">\n          No — the optical glass is colour-neutral and precision ground to avoid vignetting. Autofocus and Night Mode work exactly as normal.\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"sfaq-item\">\n        <button class=\"sfaq-btn\" type=\"button\">\n          How do I clean or store it?\n          <span class=\"sfaq-icon\">+<\/span>\n        <\/button>\n        <div class=\"sfaq-answer\">\n          Use the included microfibre pouch to wipe the lens. Store it in the protective cap when not in use. Avoid touching the glass surface directly.\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"sfaq-item\">\n        <button class=\"sfaq-btn\" type=\"button\">\n          What is your return policy?\n          <span class=\"sfaq-icon\">+<\/span>\n        <\/button>\n        <div class=\"sfaq-answer\">\n          30-day no-questions-asked returns. If you are not happy with your purchase, contact us and we will arrange a full refund or replacement.\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<script>\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.sfaq-btn').forEach(function(btn){\n  btn.addEventListener('click', function(){\n    var item = this.closest('.sfaq-item');\n    var isOpen = item.classList.contains('ope